OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,FIn Banbury, many link their
OL,7,Fexperiences to the downgrade of
OL,8,Fmaternity services at the town's
OL,9,FHorton General Hospital in 2016.
OL,11,FCampaigners say the removal of
OL,12,Fconsultant-led births has forced
OL,13,Fthousands of women to travel to Oxford
OL,14,Ffor complex care, placing increased
OL,15,Fpressure on the John Radcliffe.
