OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,FBeth Hopper, who has experienced
OL,7,Fmultiple pregnancy losses, said the
OL,8,Fvolume of concerns continues to rise.
OL,9,F"The Horton used to see around 2,000
OL,10,Fbirths a year - now it's around ten a
OL,11,Fmonth," she said.
OL,13,F"With a growing population, so many
OL,14,Fmore mothers are having to go to
OL,15,FOxford."
