OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,FIn summer 2024, Hopper created a
OL,7,Fdossier of experiences from 50
OL,8,Fdifferent women, detailing some
OL,9,Fharrowing stories of birth trauma. She
OL,10,Fsaid since then, she has had almost
OL,11,Fthe same number - enough to create a
OL,12,FPart Two.
OL,14,FDuring their meeting with Amos - who
OL,15,Fis also Master of University College
OL,16,FOxford - this week, parents said they
OL,17,Fwere given time to speak openly about
OL,18,Fwhat had happened to them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
