OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,FBeth described the atmosphere as calm
OL,7,Fand respectful, but she expressed any
OL,8,F"recommendations should also be
OL,9,Flocalised."
OL,11,FHolly Jones, from Banbury, said her
OL,12,Fpostnatal care at the John Radcliffe
OL,13,Fin December 2023 left her feeling
OL,14,F"dismissed," claiming staff focused on
OL,15,Fher past mental health history while
OL,16,Fher severe pain was not taken
OL,17,Fseriously.
OL,19,F"It wasn't until day three that the
OL,20,Fpain team saw me," she said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
