OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,F"By then my stomach was so swollen it
OL,7,Flooked like I was pregnant again."
OL,9,FHolly said the discussion with Amos
OL,10,Ffelt "cathartic" and gave her "hope
OL,11,Ffor the future", while Beth said
OL,12,Fparents were "properly listened to"
OL,13,Ffor the first time.
OL,15,FAnother parent, Keith Strangwood -
OL,16,Fwhose daughter was stillborn in 2011 -
OL,17,Fsaid hearing recent accounts from
OL,18,Fmothers during the meeting was
OL,19,F"overwhelming," adding: "I had to
OL,20,Fleave the room...it brings everything
OL,21,Fback."
