OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,FYvonne Christley, Chief Nursing
OL,7,FOfficer at Oxford University Hospitals
OL,8,FNHS Foundation Trust said: "I would
OL,9,Flike to provide assurance that all our
OL,10,Fmaternity services - including the
OL,11,Funit at John Radcliffe ` are fully
OL,12,Fstaffed and equipped with the
OL,13,Fnecessary resources and facilities for
OL,14,Fall the births we support, which is
OL,15,Faround 7,500 each year.
OL,17,F"Additionally, we have scaled up
OL,18,Finvestment significantly over the past
OL,19,F18 months, which includes successfully
OL,20,Frecruiting 54 additional midwives and
OL,21,Fbuilding a new bereavement suite.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
