OL,3,CFamilies praise meeting with Baroness
OL,4,CAmos over maternity care
OL,6,F"Overall, feedback from women and
OL,7,Ffamilies using our maternity services
OL,8,Fis good.
OL,10,F"However, we know we don't always get
OL,11,Fthings right and that we have further
OL,12,Fto go. I have read the story you
OL,13,Fshared with me about the mother who
OL,14,Fgave birth in 2023.
OL,16,F"On behalf of the Trust, I am very
OL,17,Fsorry that we have fallen short in
OL,18,Flistening to her needs at the time,
OL,19,Fand in responding with the care and
OL,20,Fsupport she needed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
